WEBVTT

00:02.726 --> 00:04.434
They make our lives a little different,...

00:05.705 --> 00:07.074
...leave us a little bit changed.

00:09.701 --> 00:12.137
So we leave behind proof of the time we spent together.

00:15.629 --> 00:17.285
They drag us into their madness,...

00:18.585 --> 00:20.340
...make us heroes in their stories.

00:23.323 --> 00:24.671
They challenge our point of view,...

00:25.737 --> 00:27.211
...push us out of what's comfortable...

00:28.337 --> 00:30.358
...and we trust them just enough to follow.

00:31.897 --> 00:34.871
But each changes us, even if just by a little.

00:35.834 --> 00:37.963
Each shifts the trajectory of our life,...

00:38.443 --> 00:40.233
...simply by being our friend.

